374
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:51,160
Have you been punished before?

375
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:53,680
I follow the rules.

376
00:20:57,199 --> 00:20:58,560
Can you tell me

377
00:20:58,599 --> 00:21:00,400
