Why haven't you done that then?

454
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:48,760
Because of you.

455
00:23:54,719 --> 00:23:56,599
Xu Guanghan is cold-blooded.

456
00:23:57,599 --> 00:23:59,079
I'm worried that once I do that,

457
00:24:00,079 --> 00:24:01,680
