We feel it.

487
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:33,520
No need for confession whatsoever.

488
00:25:33,680 --> 00:25:35,680
If you don't confess, how do you guys
know each other's feelings?

489
00:25:35,839 --> 00:25:36,680
