547
00:27:40,839 --> 00:27:42,439
I'll take my leave now.

548
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,680
Qianya.

549
00:27:50,079 --> 00:27:51,119
You pledged your house?

550
00:27:51,319 --> 00:27:52,560
What about us four then?

551
00:27:52,959 --> 00:27:53,839
Don't worry.

